{"tid":1172650,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"你地感覺上中學定大學難讀","createTime":"2019-05-26T14:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T01:23:25.000Z","uid":54930,"like":22,"dislike":91,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"55131ab43adfe8e22f9b8164fa9945140311dece","tid":1172650,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:42:27.000Z","msg":"客觀上大學野一定深過中學<br />\n<br />\n但主觀感覺上中學難過大學好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大學好多時做deadline fighter都冇問題<br />\n中學deadline先讀就炒硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又要讀自己唔鐘意既科<br />\n仲有中一岩岩轉英文又讀到PK<br />\n中三整多二科又係惡夢<br />\n仲有中五六19ies同sba <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同唔同意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d575a8dcfbdee565ddb97995ab5e4ba28842067","tid":1172650,"uid":46195,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"你試吓大學d野deadline先讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a258f1c447a4143eee462c8b83addb0af2c0ae5b","tid":1172650,"uid":197813,"like":6,"dislike":17,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"9d575a8dcfbdee565ddb97995ab5e4ba28842067","tid":1172650,"uid":46195,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"你試吓大學d野deadline先讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"我試過 但我都係覺得中學難啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"435b2ac02a838515f3cb0a8c2fdef0e5b49db255","tid":1172650,"uid":199893,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"大學又深又廣，難好多喎<br />\n中學嗰啲guide住你讀"},{"pid":"eb0d2baf990bcb8bf403d15e0065ff1d56270da1","tid":1172650,"uid":200516,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"點解中學deadline先讀就炒硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學到大學都做開deadline fighter 暫時都未出過咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec373a8d89974058cbe44ab49a11196893616652","tid":1172650,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:01:24.000Z","msg":"中學一味死背就得<br />\n大學唔得呢"},{"pid":"e5e59ff59a654311852a53108c9d878270b9778a","tid":1172650,"uid":237462,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 大學 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n大學 一科 一個SEM (三個月時間) == 成個中學DSE 課程 ＋ 深DD<br />\n大學 Deadline  先讀 準備等retake ~~<br />\n有時筆記廢要自己自修搵資料 <br />\nProject Assignment deadline fighter 準備等死 <br />\n搵到D Freeride 更加唔洗諗 （準備問候佢家人 ）<br />\n<br />\n中學 9 hea  又有guide 住黎讀 ，sba , ies 又易做 <br />\n最多一試定生死 (DSE ) ，但平時做下功課 溫下書 ，輕鬆入U <br />\n<br />\n樓主試下讀下大學 就會知中學幾撚爽"},{"pid":"fb1231a0231cd283677c9baf55b1fa80a588b44a","tid":1172650,"uid":184509,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"中學難在要返朝8晚4<br />\n真係好撚想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a366e7856e9bb2cf4a543b28c30268475d885323","tid":1172650,"uid":181581,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n13個weeks教13個topics <br />\nFinal exam 考9個topics <br />\n<br />\n中學考試考得啲咩？<br />\n黎黎去去咪又係個啲"},{"pid":"2b73149d36296079ca43aea6207b6bbb3a1db625","tid":1172650,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T19:12:53.000Z","msg":"小學"},{"pid":"3ca05b4368ef86d885d91a4638c1c350a4e49469","tid":1172650,"uid":135445,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{